if I think you are beautiful,\n   Dm                                              G\nSomeone else is going to feel it too,\n                 Dm                           G\nSo there's only one thing to do,\n\ntell you that\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nC               Am               Dm7                              G\nI've been missing you, more than words can say,\n     CM7               Am7                             Dm7        G\nAnd that Ive been thinking about it every day,\n       C                     Am7         F                                       Fm\nWell tonight's our night for dancing nice and slow,\n                  C              Am7              Dm7                 G\nBecause now I've found you, I'm never letting go,\n       C                 Am                Dm7                G  C Am Dm G7\nNo, now I've found you, I'm never letting go\n\n\n\n\n\nC               Am                Dm    G\nI've been missing you...\nC               Am               Dm    G\nI've been missing you...\nC              Am               Dm    G\nI've been missing you...\nC               Am                Dm         C\nI've been missing you, darling",
